{"id": 2799, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今评价电影，你觉得应该有哪些「评分礼仪」？", "description": "反正不是“太多五星，打个一星平衡一下”。", "record_count": 3287, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190218171348iGXynFq34zIs1UwD.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-02-25T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 330497, "content": "不上升真人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1585227}, {"id": 329739, "content": "有自己的理性判断，合理的评价，首先做一个有素质的影评者。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212385}, {"id": 329995, "content": "客观的评价 不要带有粗话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455080}, {"id": 330518, "content": "看完电影再看评分 別被评分左右\n别看到评分高就想与众不同挑毛病", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599365}, {"id": 329240, "content": "看过才有发言权", "image": null, "praise_count": 1070, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383732}, {"id": 329242, "content": "不针对演员，针对演技", "image": null, "praise_count": 379, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1123171}, {"id": 329243, "content": "没看过入门电影，没看过经典影集，等，请别瞎评分了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972975}, {"id": 329244, "content": "可以继续用昵称，但注册平台的时候实名。扒掉一层面具，展示真正的你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5109}, {"id": 329245, "content": "不要干涉其他人评分的权利，不要因为影片之外的因素而对其本身的评价产生偏倚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593421}, {"id": 329246, "content": "客观的评分态度", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 282153}, {"id": 329247, "content": "不管好与不好都理性评价，而不是一上来就先破口大骂\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974749}, {"id": 329248, "content": "只打5分和1分。5分是好评，会重刷会推荐会希望看到续作和同类作品，打1分则为了证明自己曾经“吃过一口屎”不希望别人再吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368436}, {"id": 330528, "content": "可以表达自己的观点，但是不能诋毁与自己观点不一致的所有看客。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835506}, {"id": 329249, "content": "拉踩", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515128}, {"id": 329250, "content": "我觉得按照自己想发打分比较好", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1548385}, {"id": 329253, "content": "不掺杂畸形的爱国情绪，坚决抵制脑残小粉红。", "image": null, "praise_count": 332, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593593}, {"id": 330533, "content": "客观真实", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599536}, {"id": 329254, "content": "上来就说剧情老套，看了开头就知道结尾，紧接着就差评，说浪费钱、圈钱，对于特效，演员演技等优点全部抹灭的影评人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564719}, {"id": 329255, "content": "看过再说，憋瞎BB", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389808}, {"id": 329256, "content": "言辞犀利，不是刻薄。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593618}, {"id": 329257, "content": "不要一味地比较，而忽略进步性。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972975}, {"id": 330537, "content": "冷静的看完电影，不要管别人怎么说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950237}, {"id": 329258, "content": "特效", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1585625}, {"id": 329259, "content": "能允许不同的意见，不跑去他人的影评大谈特谈自己的看法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417126}, {"id": 329260, "content": "豆瓣也有一部分瞎评瞎喷的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1585164}, {"id": 330540, "content": "别因为自己不喜欢就去否定", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599616}, {"id": 329261, "content": "猜不到结局加分 刻意煽情减分", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580520}, {"id": 329262, "content": "友善的语言是交流的起点", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1589030}, {"id": 329263, "content": "人人口味不同，尽量避免主观臆断和没有根据的推理", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593646}, {"id": 329264, "content": "真实感受，有根有据", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593646}, {"id": 329520, "content": "不要无脑黑，实事求是。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1587777}, {"id": 329265, "content": "有理有据有节", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174535}, {"id": 329266, "content": "各抒己见，不要撕逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593653}, {"id": 329267, "content": "赞美自己喜欢的作品！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311674}, {"id": 329268, "content": "不被政治正确裹挟", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467319}, {"id": 330804, "content": "少点杠精，多点平和", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598696}, {"id": 329272, "content": "给极端分要慎重", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534883}, {"id": 329273, "content": "反对（明明没看就开始：）实至名归", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482982}, {"id": 329274, "content": "基本还是想要理性，但是我觉得忠于内心最重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441232}, {"id": 329530, "content": "想一想究竟是自己看不下去，还是电影不好。不要因为别人觉得好看而不好意思说不好看，也不要因为别人不喜欢而不好意思说喜欢。尊重每个人的评分。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310603}, {"id": 329275, "content": "从多方面客观评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593668}, {"id": 329277, "content": "允许批评，别把对于电影和演技的批评当做对导演和演员的人身攻击", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 329278, "content": "根据自己的实际情况和对影评的理解打分", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565012}, {"id": 329279, "content": "评了也写一下观感吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054974}, {"id": 329280, "content": "在未评分前…\n不应该看到评价的分数…", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1563008}, {"id": 329281, "content": "🚫刷分。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156685}, {"id": 329282, "content": "明明就不是专业评委的普通人却要装作读懂了一切似的对一部电影评头论足，什么特效不到位，剧情不紧凑~更要命的是结尾总有这么几句:个人观点，不喜勿喷。这不是喷子是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499146}, {"id": 330562, "content": "有偏见还不如不看不评分", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599886}, {"id": 335682, "content": "别那么刻薄，有的时候影评人是站着说话不腰疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619389}, {"id": 329285, "content": "好好评价，不要撕", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593764}]}